{
  "stem": "4345.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, would you like to have this bread?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN]?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, this would be very nice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he says to me, I'll give you the bread if you go to sleep with me in the scheune, if I go to sleep with him in the barn.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, [INAUDIBLE], coming from the home such as I, with such a strong sense of morality, just like I spoke at the table, you know, and I said to myself, what is one to do?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if he's going to take me and rape me-- I had no idea it would rape was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was so totally ignorant and so stupid on that subject.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When did I ever learn about sex at home?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "How old were you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You could not even bring the word 'sex' into your mouth in front of a mommy and a daddy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We learned in-- Bais Yaakov, in Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our teacher, this was taught to us in the proper way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't come in [INAUDIBLE] having sex.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This will be-- oh God, I wouldn't even dare.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to him, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You would like to sleep with a filthy pig Jew?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said to him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Isn't it enough that you slaughtering my family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN] I said to him, my whole family is dead from your hands, I said, slaughtered.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN] I said now you want me, a filthy pig that has lice on her body and that is sick, sleep with me?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, you try to touch me, I said, and you are dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, [INAUDIBLE], I don't know if you ever encountered the-- the [SPEAKING HEBREW], God's-- God's strength that he sends a certain strength into you.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
